{
  "texts": [
    "The future of education around the world will be greatly impacted by this type of technology (Renz and Hilbig, 2020; Ji et al., 2023; Mäkitalo et al., 2023).",
    "Regarding the Brazilian case, the educational landscape reflects a diverse and multifaceted system comprising public and private schools, each addressing distinct regional characteristics and challenges.",
    "Despite the adoption of modern pedagogical approaches, traditional assessment methods have long dominated the evaluation process.",
    "In this scenario, as the significance of student assessments remains central to the effectiveness of educational practices, the exploration of innovative AI technologies (such as ChatGPT) presents a compelling avenue for potential advancements in this domain.",
    "There is a growing recognition that assessment strategies must evolve in line with contemporary learning paradigms."
  ]
}